s, stockholder challenges under Delaware law, seeking to prevent the Texas =
Redomestication.=E2=80=9D We have talked about this possibility before. The=
 theory is roughly: =E2=80=9CDelaware law protects minority shareholders fr=
om the whimsical acts of controlling shareholders like Elon Musk. In partic=
ular, it just protected=C2=A0the shareholders from that $56 billion pay pac=
kage. Now Elon Musk, Tesla=E2=80=99s controlling shareholder, is trying to =
