ware law must protect minority shareholders from that outcome. Therefore, D=
elaware law must=C2=A0prevent Tesla from reincorporating in Texas.=E2=80=9D=
This theory strikes me as hilarious, unlikely, but also logically consisten=
t; I don=E2=80=99t think you can entirely rule it out. When we first discus=
sed it, though, we were awaiting a ruling in a lawsuit trying to block Trip=
Advisor Inc.=E2=80=99s reincorporation from Delaware to Nevada. Since then,=
