ink that was a good idea.Why? Here are three possibilities:=09Maybe Texas c=
orporate law=C2=A0protects minority shareholders in roughly the same way th=
at Delaware law does, so=C2=A0this is=C2=A0not a big deal. Maybe=C2=A0the m=
ove to Texas has nothing to do with Musk=E2=80=99s pay package or his desir=
e for control; perhaps it=E2=80=99s a pure coincidence. Tesla=E2=80=99s pro=
xy statement, I wrote in April, =E2=80=9Cgoes out of its way to say, no, we=
=E2=80=99re not just moving to Texas so we can pay Musk more, what ever gav=
