ate, which were often developed in academia and pioneered over decades by t=
he likes of AQR Capital Management and Dimensional Fund Advisors.</p><p sty=
le=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Yet money managers are increasingly giving in to the=
 sheer convenience of QIS. ...</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Uses vary, b=
ut in a typical case a fixed-income team at a multi-strategy hedge fund mig=
ht trade stock options with QIS. Or a firm that=E2=80=99s never done commod=
ities might utilize them to quickly add some exposure to raw materials.</p>=
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CTo multi-pod type of hedge funds, QIS=
