eam doesn=E2=80=99t have trading capabilities, said Arnaud Jobert, the co-h=
ead of global strategic indices at JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co., which runs a n=
otional $85 billion in the business.=C2=A0</p></blockquote><p style=3D"marg=
