m-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; bac=
kground-color: #ccc;">chess grandmaster</a>=C2=A0is probably a lot lower th=
an the cost of employing a good quantitative trader.</p><p style=3D"margin:=
 16px 0;">In somewhat related news, here is a Wall Street Journal story abo=
ut <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/35707099.259299=
